Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetransactions

package it.polimi.ingsw.common.backend.model.resourcetransactions
This package contains the implementation of the resource transactions of Masters of Renaissance.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ProductionRequest
    This class represents the request of a production, i.e. a resource transaction request allowing the use of only strongboxes as output containers.
    ResourceTransaction
    This class represents a transaction of resources.
    ResourceTransactionRecipe
    This class represents a recipe of a transaction of transfers of resources from and to resource containers and a player.
    ResourceTransactionRequest
    This class represents a resource transaction request.
